        # nr.sumtype
        
        Sumtypes in Python.
        
        ### Example
        
        ```python
        from nr.sumtype import Constructor, Sumtype
        
        class Status(Sumtype):
          Idle = Constructor()
          Loading = Constructor(['progress'])
          Succeeded = Constructor()
          Error = Constructor(['message'])
        
        print(Status.Loading(progress=0.0))
        ```
        
